{"tid":396212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同屋企人去梗旅行 好撚崩潰","createTime":"2017-09-11T13:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T15:40:51.000Z","uid":126809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2451a63bc5894ac469b69f2681ede243a20d3cbd","tid":396212,"uid":126809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"唉 去七日旅行 而家先第三日 就嚟頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我老豆成日自以為事 覺得自己一定岩晒 寧願信自己直覺 都唔信google map 搞到係三日入面不停帶錯我哋行路 最尾都係要我哋睇翻google map帶佢行翻一條岩嘅路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢成日心大心細 諗唔定食咩 之後我哋就比啲意見 佢又話唔好 再加上言語不通 搞到平均每次點餐都最起碼要10分鐘先搞掂<br />\n<br />\n佢一飲咗酒就會開始發癲 不停係到街嗰到大嗌 搞到啲路人用一個極度不屑嘅眼神望過嚟 我見到都覺得好老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f06a031adbeb4fbd7d85ecd630852da28fbc0e","tid":396212,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:28:36.000Z","msg":"點餐"},{"pid":"0a965a08fbe4bf3ffc53691420ac78a16a8ab5f0","tid":396212,"uid":72946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"我依家都係wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好你少少 但都唔好得去邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4018a85ff8de4add49d850ee6e13647de1c7452c","tid":396212,"uid":126811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"我老豆都係咁 唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f164c2f4b2b3a942d3742cb5024a2dca2d92f5d","tid":396212,"uid":82411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:31:04.000Z","msg":"同屋企人去乜撚自由行呀<br />\n跟團咪算囉"},{"pid":"c449c4d692ea862b4cdfe9eb4311d0f256f6cc16","tid":396212,"uid":53165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:33:35.000Z","msg":"同你差唔多，上過帶兩老去日本，我老豆係都信自己唔信個google map ,  我忍唔住 叫跟我行，行到咪知唔個真，最後e家佢變左有玩google map 玩上癮 ，有時落街食個tea 都要開google map<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6424215a5a5b1df5bad8ca6eb9325cedd20516db","tid":396212,"uid":126809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你差唔多，上過帶兩老去日本，我老豆係都信自己唔信個google map ,  我忍唔住 叫跟我行，行到咪知唔個真，最後e家佢變左有玩google map 玩上癮 ，有時落街食個tea 都要開google map<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔明佢哋點諗 以為去咗幾日就當自己住咗係嗰到幾十年 識晒啲路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea99016c37862cd419e9166b928e363b11b0f4f6","tid":396212,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"唔係唔跟團嘛？<br />\n<br />\n兩老去完旅行番黎好開心<br />\n跟團坐郵輪<br />\n<br />\n黎緊諗住再比佢地去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c86baf6ea1dcfb173fa02dfccda90e6f1e3c73","tid":396212,"uid":1495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同屋企人去乜撚自由行呀<br />\n跟團咪算囉</blockquote><br />\n呢個真"},{"pid":"971b627b0ac6ca7aefbc05760036ecf6ba6628d7","tid":396212,"uid":126809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同屋企人去乜撚自由行呀<br />\n跟團咪算囉</blockquote><br />\n呢個真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前跟團要成日勁早起身 頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb74012d8139c5470424da56b5d0f8040e6c4385","tid":396212,"uid":137783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:21:58.000Z","msg":"吊我老豆同你老豆完全相反 上次全家去日本旅行 佢勁信google map 去到Jr站入面重堅持用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明已經有路牌指示"},{"pid":"ccb3f8a4c3e204bcfd9efa4e18fad40b3128d950","tid":396212,"uid":81867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T15:40:51.000Z","msg":"祝你好運 2次同屋企人出去旅行<br />\n一次當地嘈餐勁 一次自己想喊<br />\n